multi tab view allows us to have multiple tabs open at the same time

need to keep track of which ports used and available so a list of web sockets to maintain

keep track of status of missions, in progress, completed, closed abruptly
in progress means the socket is still connected
completed means we succesfuly finished and exited the run
closed abruptly means the program closed/exited out

if its in progress we can go back and press live view to continue, hard part will be reloading all the information that was being logged
or mapping the in progress to an existing data buffer / index in memory

